arStrings.szText: You misunderstand. I come to offer you a way to aid her. She is dying. But she doesn’t need to. She will survive, if she frees me from the stone.
The prophecy speaks true: my brothers are coming. And when they arrive, they will not bargain with you, wanderer. You will not defeat them. Not alone.
We were formidable allies in Hell. Our partnership could yet bear fruit.
Talk to Neyrelle, when you reach her. Offer her this relief. You let her choose me once—she may yet choose me again.
